<p>It all starts with hiring the right person for the right job. And Iâ€™m not talking about competencies only. <a href="https://blog.teammood.com/2019/02/19/hire-for-culture-fit-not-competencies.html">Culture fit</a> is one of the key criteria â€“ if not the most important â€“ to infuse a feeling of belonging to your team members.</p>

